### Signup
POST http://localhost:5050/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Test User
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="age"

21
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="phone"

9876543210
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="email"

test@example.com
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="password"

test123
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="idProof"; filename="id.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample-id.png
------boundary--

### Login
POST http://localhost:5050/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:5050/api/auth/logout

### Create a booking
POST http://localhost:5050/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventName": "Birthday Party",
  "package": "Premium",
  "date": "2026-07-15"
}

### Check availability for the month
GET http://localhost:5050/api/bookings/availability?month=2026-07

### Get my bookings
GET http://localhost:5050/api/bookings/my-bookings